# Risk-accepted CVEs for this vendor image. Each line must carry an
# expiry date and a ticket reference — Trivy suppresses only the
# listed IDs, everything else keeps failing loudly.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # expiry:YYYY-MM-DD  ticket:SEC-XXXX  reason:<short>
#
# Populate after the first SARIF upload lands in Code Scanning.
# Renovate/Dependabot will bump the pinned tag when the vendor ships
# a patched release — clear the corresponding line here at that time.
